Package: wlstatus
Architecture: any
Maintainer: steven66619 <ste@example.com>
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/steven66619/wlstatus-new
Depends: libcairo2, libpango-1.0-0, libpangocairo-1.0-0,
 libwayland-client0, libglib2.0-0, libharfbuzz0b,
 libpixman-1-0, libpng16-16, liblua5.4-0
Description: Lightweight Wayland status bar with Lua plugin support
 A lightweight status bar for Hyprland, Sway, and other wlr-layer-shell
 compositors. Features Lua plugins for CPU, memory, disk, volume,
 network, battery, and updates, plus workspace switching and power
 options with confirmation popup.
